<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>CK Lottery Predictor</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; background: #f4f4f9; }
    h1 { color: #333; }
    button { padding: 10px 20px; margin: 10px; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 8px; border: none; background: #4CAF50; color: white; cursor: pointer; }
    button:hover { background: #45a049; }
    #result { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #222; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>CK Lottery Predictor (Demo)</h1>
  <p>နောက်ထွက်မယ့် နံပါတ်ကို ခန့်မှန်းကြည့်ပါ</p>
  <button onclick="predict()"> Predict Now</button>
  <div id="result"></div>

  <script>
    function predict() {
      const numbers = Math.floor(Math.random() * 10); // 0-9 random
      const bigSmall = numbers >= 5 ? "Big" : "Small";
      document.getElementById("result").innerText = "Prediction: " + numbers + " (" + bigSmall + ")";
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
 
